thread.title: Alex
thread.title_full: Wall Art Prints reviewed by Alex

author: Alex
title: Alex
text: The arts are excellent, hanged on the wall they look beautiful. However extremely disappointed with the delivery service. Stayed for 2 days at home waiting for the delivery and at the end of the second day only got notifications (not even a pickup card in the letter box) that I need to collect my delivery from the local post office that in my case is 20 min walking distance each way. I have 10 months old baby and no car co had to carry the baby and push the pram with the arts in it wich was extremely hard and not something i was planning to do when I shopped online
